He was asked in effect, to
take on a role of photographer

00:35:03.480 --> 00:35:06.070
in the residence, in
the hope that some day,

00:35:06.070 --> 00:35:10.040
such a position might
officially be designated.

00:35:11.610 --> 00:35:18.950
Here is an energized Bob, during
