00:35:40.950 --> 00:35:46.090
You've already seen his most famous
photograph in Birmingham Spring,

00:35:46.090 --> 00:35:50.050
1963, and he was there

00:35:50.050 --> 00:35:52.880
and he witnessed how the
students wouldn't run away,

00:35:52.880 --> 00:35:57.020
holding on to each
other for their lives.

00:35:57.020 --> 00:36:01.390
Bob's teacher, Alexey Brodovitch
claimed this image; quote,

00:36:01.390 --> 00:36:05.310
