00:36:05.310 --> 00:36:08.750
Bob did not have much formal
training in photography;

00:36:08.750 --> 00:36:11.920
his real introduction
was through his father,

00:36:11.920 --> 00:36:16.660
who was a serious amateur
with a dark room at home.

00:36:16.660 --> 00:36:20.340 position:56%
Bob attended Manhattan's [inaudible]
in high school, and then [inaudible]

00:36:20.340 --> 00:36:24.510
for a master's degree at
Columbia, he majored in Philosophy,

00:36:24.510 --> 00:36:27.180
as we've heard, focusing
on aesthetics,

00:36:27.180 --> 00:36:30.000
and continued studying about art.

00:36:30.000 --> 00:36:32.960
He spent a year at
law school at Harvard,

00:36:32.960 --> 00:36:37.130
