and began talking his way

00:36:37.130 --> 00:36:39.630
into photographer studios.

00:36:39.630 --> 00:36:43.360
Eventually, in 1959 he enrolled

00:36:43.360 --> 00:36:45.480
in [inaudible] famous
design laboratory,

00:36:45.480 --> 00:36:49.410
at the new school for
social research.

00:36:49.410 --> 00:36:53.120
For an assignment, to
shoot in Times Square,

00:36:53.120 --> 00:36:58.470
