he took a graphical look down,

00:36:58.470 --> 00:37:02.000
on a group of sailors
from the hotel Astor.

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:05.540
For the assignment,
to photograph an egg,

00:37:05.540 --> 00:37:09.020
