00:48:28.860 --> 00:48:32.870
Actually, this image revels
-- or reveals, I should say --

00:48:32.870 --> 00:48:37.400
Bob's delight in technology
and humanity.

00:48:37.400 --> 00:48:43.390 position:56%
He has manipulated his camera, so
