in order to view a film about
design in the technological age.

00:49:04.750 --> 00:49:12.770
Bob's career epitomizes what Ralph
Ellison said about his work, quote,

00:49:12.770 --> 00:49:18.090
"It moves into the rear sneer,
where in technical ability

00:49:18.090 --> 00:49:23.930
and social vision combined
to create a work of art."

00:49:23.930 --> 00:49:27.890
His archive now joins
forces with the Library

00:49:27.890 --> 00:49:31.890
