American creators.

00:49:43.010 --> 00:49:46.240
His work will continue
to have a place

00:49:46.240 --> 00:49:51.650
in American history alongside
his heroes, and ours.

00:49:51.650 --> 00:49:58.040
We can just imagine that the
ever smiling, serious, wild,

